p:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/b95e4/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 256w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/1779b/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 512w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/87945/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 1024w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/5a523/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/b95e4/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 256w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/1779b/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 512w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/87945/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 1024w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/5a523/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/87945/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/b95e4/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 256w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/1779b/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 512w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/87945/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 1024w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/5a523/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/b95e4/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 256w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/1779b/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 512w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/87945/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 1024w,\n/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/5a523/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/877c201b21004939ef7e49f7dcb609cd/87945/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Over the last 6-8 months, The PM Group’s agency clients have experienced some amazing accomplishments! For example, ‘<em>The Freaky Car Show’</em> we produced at <strong><a href=\"https://www.sixflags.com/fiestatexas\">Six Flags Fiesta Texas</a></strong> last October for four weeks led to the park to being #1 in the country for attendance.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, as written in a previous post on our site, the San Antonio area <strong><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/agency-news/sales-records-are-made-to-be-broken-part-1/\">IHOP restaurants</a></strong> had 2-consecutive weeks of ALL-TIME record sales in March. ‘Wow!’ is really an understatement when you consider we are still in the dark shadow of the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>But this accomplishment is even more rewarding and amazing!</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>The PM Group created a museum exhibit for the <strong><a href=\"https://www.samuseum.org/\">San Antonio Museum of Art</a></strong> (SAMA) called ‘Movie Metal’ that opened in late February and was scheduled to run through April 11, 2021. The exhibit realized RECORD BREAKING attendance, and as a result of SAMA’s success, the exhibit has been now extended until June 20, 2021.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/agency-news/san-antonio-museum-of-art-celebrates-40th-anniversary-with-movie-metal-exhibit/\">SAMA’s ‘Movie Metal’</a></strong> exhibit is an action-packed display of metallic heroes and vehicles from some of Hollywood’s most popular movies and TV shows. There are Batmobiles and a DeLorean time machine. You can also see the actual F-1 race car that Tony Stark, aka Iron Man, drove in the IRON MAN 2 movie. You’ll also find Transformers’ ‘<em>Bumblebee</em>’ and ‘<em>Optimus Prime</em>’ towering tall in SAMA’s museum lobby too!</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed aligncenter is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Movie Metal Extended\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oRtscZgL-y4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\"><strong>About The PM Group</strong></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 33 years, the agency has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profits, real estate and fitness. For two consecutive years now, the Agency has set annual revenue records with the addition of six new clients and through the continued success of our existing clients. Additionally, the agency hosts their annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In 2020 alone, the Agency donated over $1,050,000 to local non-profits. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"Sales Records Are Made to Be Broken—Part 2","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Sales Records Are Made to Be Broken—Part 2","url":"/sales-records-are-made-to-be-broken-part-2/"}],"title":"Sales Records Are Made to Be Broken—Part 2 | The PM Group","metaDesc":"The PM Group created a museum exhibit for the San Antonio Museum of Art (SAMA) called ‘Movie Metal’ that has been now extended until June 20, 2021...","focuskw":"San Antonio Museum of Art","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Sales Records Are Made to Be Broken—Part 2 | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"The PM Group created a museum exhibit for the San Antonio Museum of Art (SAMA) called ‘Movie Metal’ that has been now extended until June 20, 2021...","opengraphImage":{"altText":"San Antonio Museum of Art Movie Metal - The PM Group San Antonio Advertising Agency","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan-300x158.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan-768x403.jpg 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MM-Extended-Date-1200x630-IronMan.jpg 1200w"},"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/sales-records-are-made-to-be-broken-part-2/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u